SmartKanaConverter is a string converter like mb_convert_kana
function in PHP that converts japanese fullwidth/halfwidth
Hiragana/Katakana mutualy.

INSTALLATION

  1. copy src/* into your project.
  2. add SmartKanaConverter.[hm] into your project.
     SmartKanaConverter_*.m files can't to be compiled individually and don't add.


USAGE

  see test/TestSmartKanaConverter.m


CONVERSION RULES

  see src/SmartKanaConverter_init.m
